steps.name: "Find Contact" window opens and click Add button
Enter Contact_Id and enter First_Name and enter Middle_Name
Enter Last_Name and Enter Suffix and enter Description
Click Save button and click Add button next to Facilities grid
Enter "My Lab" and click Find button
Click OK button on the Contacts screen
Find "Last Name" by entering Last Name and click Find button
Click OK button and "Edit Contact" window opens
